                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-849-18540703 t18540703-849-punishment-41"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
